{"tid":2228201,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[駱惠寧劏房騷 ] 真正身分為「護旗手」　定期清理「連儂牆」","createTime":"2020-10-03T11:13:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T12:58:13.000Z","uid":224066,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"75e1de78f94603bf61727c2321ae3448b532c3be","tid":2228201,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:13:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Oc8vlOZZzUU7Ad86i-QzHAskm7A=/802x976/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RJ3CDH6YCBFSTI4DREATZDIGSI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FOc8vlOZZzUU7Ad86i-QzHAskm7A%3D%2F802x976%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRJ3CDH6YCBFSTI4DREATZDIGSI.jpg&h=3147e0b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任駱惠寧日前以「第二管治隊伍」姿態，探訪了兩戶所謂「基層市民」，當中包括深水埗劏房戶徐天民。有眼利的網民發現，徐天民早就在官媒的報道中以受訪者身份出現，質疑他是官方「臨時演員」。本報進一步發現，徐天民其實是知名「護旗手」，多次參與撐警集會和清連儂牆行動；他的住處也相當飄忽，時而以「觀塘市民」身份出現，時而深水埗。<br />\n<br />\n內媒多次報道<br />\n駱惠寧日前到訪徐天民面積不足八平方米的劏房，二人坐在碌架床下格交談，徐天民聲稱自己目前失業，妻女被迫返回鄉下湖南生活。有網民發現，今年1月1日《北京日報》有關金紫荊廣場升旗儀式的報道中，徐天民早就以深水埗市民「徐先生」身份接受訪問。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EO30Rrclz24xLkpGwGIM--HdvPk=/802x601/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/O3N5AOK6VBFYJFEAN3VIYUU2WE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEO30Rrclz24xLkpGwGIM--HdvPk%3D%2F802x601%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FO3N5AOK6VBFYJFEAN3VIYUU2WE.jpg&h=d4025b6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n記者翻查資料發現，徐天民其實是知名「護旗手」，經常出現在中國網媒的報道中。早在去年8月17日，徐就被「環球網」拍到手持中國國旗參加添馬公園的撐警集會，後來他接受訪問，聲稱自己去年6月見到激進勢力的行為後「特別氣憤」，曾一個人手持國旗。由深水埗步行到元朗、屯門再折返，「全程30公里」（Google map顯示，來回深水埗和元朗約70多公里）。<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p843x403/120346395_3331227550246465_8217821853404363178_n.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_ohc=NS2FZWbhqSoAX_Bn7M4&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=bca83fe37817a6700c694e3942759459&amp;oe=5F9ED0FC\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp843x403%2F120346395_3331227550246465_8217821853404363178_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_ohc%3DNS2FZWbhqSoAX_Bn7M4%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26tp%3D6%26oh%3Dbca83fe37817a6700c694e3942759459%26oe%3D5F9ED0FC&h=a4db18f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n徐天民又參與過各式愛國遊行，包括由「觀塘市民」發起到美國領事館的抗議行動，並且多次到警署送禮。他聲稱會定期和同伴在晚上清理連儂牆，並張貼「愛港愛國」標語。<span class=\"red\">今年5月26日國歌法二讀前夕，他和好友自發組隊到立法會大樓外「保衞立法會」，聲稱成功嚇退「黑衣人小隊」，足足留守了48小時。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Zy8CV25elSHb2cqOkCKDVu-hfN8=/802x1069/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3RSJ4YEMFBDLFK2RE6YYFY2ZNE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZy8CV25elSHb2cqOkCKDVu-hfN8%3D%2F802x1069%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3RSJ4YEMFBDLFK2RE6YYFY2ZNE.jpg&h=7c0e15e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但愛國似乎未能保障他生活富足。徐天民在訪問中聲稱自己2013年來港，及後在某酒店擔任飲食主管，但被起底後就被酒店辭退，全家失業。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-10-0220E4B88BE58D885.56.23_GDFv6_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE89EA2E5B995E688AAE59C96202020-10-0220E4B88BE58D885.56.23_GDFv6_1200x0.png&h=2f15580b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網上誤傳為《北京日報》記者<br />\n<br />\n徐天民被《北京日報》訪問的照片今日在網上流傳，由於拍攝角度仿似由徐天民自行拿著咪說話「做扒」，故不少網民質疑他真正身分是記者，留言指「又和戲子做戲欺騙人」、「大陸宣傳品，唔使咁認真」等等。但在騰訊網內的另一相片則顯示，其實當時有另一名男子為他拿著咪，徐天民應正在受訪。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/tsui-20_Rte1d_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Ftsui-20_Rte1d_1200x0.png&h=1f3739a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f1cd740b4d4ac233bef06b084fd3901f4b0acce","tid":2228201,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77322fab294b2cdea44ee8212f9c7b3b185624d2","tid":2228201,"uid":237300,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ed754f956fb5b9dac5a342d47d5240b042273d","tid":2228201,"uid":76261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:53:07.000Z","msg":"作為一個護旗手，係屋企有支國旗係好合理，都唔知你地嘈乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9151f73397ee9c8704ec248db7c7080046c3bc","tid":2228201,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:09:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0453ee8f33bf952dfb837974d8221cec17e69566","tid":2228201,"uid":24457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:12:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38bab8306591414365f5a53b16080d0bafa207f","tid":2228201,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}